ed="T" n="0780b18"/><persName key="A003636">釋大安</persName>，姓<name>陳</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000017166">閩城</placeName><ptr target="#n1619"/>人也。幼年入道，頓拂<lb
ed="T" n="0780b19"/>塵蒙<ptr target="#n1620"/>。<date from-iso="+0817-01-25" key="j20194882019871" to-iso="+0818-02-12"><name>元和</name>十二年</date>，勅<placeName key="PL000000017141"><placeName>建州</placeName><placeName>浦城縣</placeName><placeName>乾元寺</placeName></placeName>置<lb
ed="T" n="0780b20"/><placeName key="PL000000057067">兜率壇</placeName>，始全戒足。時天雨桂子及地生朱<lb
ed="T" n="0780b21"/>草，刺史<persName key="A010575">元錫</persName>手疏其瑞，上達<ref type="person" target="#A002120">冕旒</ref>，遂迴御<lb
ed="T" n="0780b22"/><anchor xml:id="beg0780002"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>禮</sic><corr>札</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0780002"/>，詔改<placeName key="PL000000017141">鳳棲寺</placeName>號<placeName key="PL000000057067">靈感壇</placeName>焉。<persName key="A003636">安</persName>因往<placeName key="PL000000018628">洪<lb
ed="T" n="0780b23"/>井</placeName>，路出<placeName key="PL000000008820">上元</placeName>，忽逢一老父曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A003636">子</ref>往<placeName key="PL000000018628">南昌</placeName>，必<lb
ed="T" n="0780b24"/>有所<anchor xml:id="beg0780003"/>得<anchor xml:id="end0780003"/>。」及咨參律學，夜聞二僧談論，遽<lb
ed="T" n="0780b25"/>了三乘之旨，乃以所習付之同人<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1592"/>。之<placeName key="PL000000019846">臨川</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0780b26"/>見<placeName key="PL000000019958">石鞏山</placeName><persName key="A010576">慧藏<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>。<persName key="A010576">藏</persName>之提唱，必持弓弩以<lb
ed="T" n="0780b27"/>擬學人。<persName key="A003636">安</persName><anchor xml:id="beg0780004"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>服</sic><corr>膜</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0780004"/>拜未興，唱曰：「看箭。」<persName key="A003636">安</persName>神色<lb
ed="T" n="0780b28"/>不撓，答對不差。<persName key="A010576">石鞏</persName>乃投弩曰：「幾年射，始<lb
ed="T" n="0780b29"/>中半人也矣。」<persName key="A003636">安</persName>遊<placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺</placeName>，入<placeName key="PL000000005248">龍池</placeName>沐浴，雖<pb ed="T" n="0780c" xml:id="T50.2061.0780c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0780c01"/>久寖漣漪，殊無奮暴雨雹之怪，觀者驚悚。<lb
ed="T" n="0780c02"/>後止<placeName key="PL000000028694">溈山</placeName>，<anchor xml:id="beg0780sgsz10"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0780sgsz10"/><persName key="A001984">大圓禪師</persName>，復證前聞而為量<lb
ed="T" n="0780c03"/>果<ptr type="glossary" target="#g258"/>也。時<placeName key="PL000000018603">豫章</placeName>廉使贈太<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>尉</sic><corr>師</corr></choice><persName key="A022982">崔貞孝<roleName>公</roleName></persName>，則<persName key="A022535">魏公</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0780c04"/>之季父<ptr target="#n1621"/>，深契玄機，敦<persName key="A003636">安</persName>之道，飛疏召之，厥<lb
ed="T" n="0780c05"/>譽愈昌。<date from-iso="+0873-02-05" key="j20399532040307" to-iso="+0874-01-25"><name>咸通</name>十四年</date>，詔宜號<persName key="A003636">延聖大師</persName>，賜<lb
ed="T" n="0780c06"/>紫袈裟一副。<date from-iso="+0882-01-27" key="j20432312043614" to-iso="+0883-02-14"><name>中和</name>二年</date>示疾，所止法堂巨梁<lb
ed="T" n="0780c07"/>中折。<date key="j20439022043902" when-iso="+0883-11-29">三年癸卯十月二十二日</date>，坐化于<placeName key="PL000000017203">怡山</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0780c08"/>丈室，春秋九十一，臘六十七。續詔贈<persName key="A003636">圓智大<lb
ed="T" n="0780c09"/>師</persName>，塔號<placeName key="PL000000057073">證真</placeName><ptr target="#n1622"/>。<persName key="A003636">安</persName>不嘗唾地，不處溫房，隨<lb
ed="T" n="0780c10"/>化而衣，天雨而<anchor xml:id="beg0780005"/>浴<anchor xml:id="end0780005"/>。諮法弟子<persName key="A010579">慧長</persName>入<placeName key="PL000000042002">關</placeName>，揚<lb
ed="T" n="0780c11"/><persName key="A003636">安</persName>之德，故有追謚也。<placeName key="PL000000002513">博陵</placeName><ref type="person" target="#A022982">司空相國</ref><ptr target="#n1623"/>仰慕<lb
ed="T" n="0780c12"/>前烈，遂著文頌德。詩人<persName key="A010580">周朴</persName>篤重<persName key="A003636">安</persName>，時入<lb
ed="T" n="0780c13"/>山致<anchor xml:id="beg0780sgsz12"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0780sgsz12"/>焉。</p>
